{"title":"富强","date":"2021-01-07T02:13:57.684Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 7, 2021","L":"01/07/2021","MM-DD":"01-07"},"thumbnail":"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2021/20210107101050.png","link":"2021/01/07/富强","updated":"2021-01-07T02:12:21.922Z","content":"<h1 id=\"富强\">富强<a title=\"#富强\" href=\"#富强\"></a></h1>\n<h4 id=\"一、为什么要富强\">一、为什么要富强<a title=\"#一、为什么要富强\" href=\"#一、为什么要富强\"></a></h4>\n<p>因为 <font color=\"#dd0000\">富强、民主、文明、和谐，倡导自由、平等、公正、法治，倡导爱国、敬业、诚信、友善</font></p>\n<h4 id=\"二、富强有什么作用\">二、富强有什么作用<a title=\"#二、富强有什么作用\" href=\"#二、富强有什么作用\"></a></h4>\n<p><font color=\"#dd00dd\">科学、ML</font></p>\n<p>三、富强结构</p>\n<ul>\n<li>v2ray</li>\n<li>websocket + tls</li>\n<li>Nginx</li>\n<li>Cloudflare CDN</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>开始操作</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"一、安装v2ray（这里针对windows端，因为我小鸡dd了windwos）\">一、安装v2ray（这里针对Windows端，因为我小鸡DD了windwos）<a title=\"#一、安装v2ray（这里针对windows端，因为我小鸡dd了windwos）\" href=\"#一、安装v2ray（这里针对windows端，因为我小鸡dd了windwos）\"></a></h3>\n<p>下载v2ray  <a href=\"https://github.com/v2ray/v2ray-core/\" target=\"_blank\">飞机直达详情页</a></p>\n<p>选择下载  <a href=\"https://github.com/v2ray/v2ray-core/releases/download/v4.28.2/v2ray-windows-64.zip\" target=\"_blank\">v2ray-windows-64.zip</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2021/20210106174605.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p>这里有运行的脚本，粘贴以下字符到记事本里，重命名成<strong>start.bat</strong>，将此文件复制到  <strong>v2ray-windows-64.zip</strong>解压后的文件夹里，以管理员运行即可</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">@echo off</span><br><span class=\"line\">title v2ray启动脚本</span><br><span class=\"line\">color 0a</span><br><span class=\"line\">start &quot;v2ray&quot; &quot;%~dp0\\wv2ray.exe&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">tasklist &#x2F;fi &quot;imagename eq wv2ray.exe&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">echo.</span><br><span class=\"line\">echo.</span><br><span class=\"line\">echo 程序启动成功！按任意键关闭本窗口</span><br><span class=\"line\">echo.</span><br><span class=\"line\">pause</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>粘贴以下字符到记事本里，重命名成<strong>stop.bat</strong>，复制到文件夹里，管理员运行即可停止v2ray</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">@echo off</span><br><span class=\"line\">title v2ray停止脚本</span><br><span class=\"line\">color 0a</span><br><span class=\"line\">echo.</span><br><span class=\"line\">tasklist|findstr &quot;wv2ray.exe&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">echo.</span><br><span class=\"line\">taskkill &#x2F;f &#x2F;im wv2ray.exe</span><br><span class=\"line\">pause</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后修改v2ray的配置 config.json，这里有两种配置 一种是可以ML的，一种是可以套CDN加速的，这里以第二种为主</p>\n<p>免流的配置（tcp+http）：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br><span class=\"line\">74</span><br><span class=\"line\">75</span><br><span class=\"line\">76</span><br><span class=\"line\">77</span><br><span class=\"line\">78</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &quot;log&quot; : &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;access&quot;: &quot;E:\\\\Log\\\\access.log&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;error&quot;: &quot;E:\\\\Log\\\\error.log&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;loglevel&quot;: &quot;warning&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &quot;inbound&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;port&quot;: 6666,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;protocol&quot;: &quot;vmess&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;settings&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;clients&quot;: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;id&quot;: &quot;你的UUID&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;level&quot;: 1,</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;alterId&quot;: 1</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      ]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;streamSettings&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;network&quot;: &quot;tcp&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;tcpSettings&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;header&quot;: &#123; </span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;type&quot;: &quot;http&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;response&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;version&quot;: &quot;1.1&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;status&quot;: &quot;200&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;reason&quot;: &quot;OK&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;headers&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">              &quot;Content-Type&quot;: [&quot;application&#x2F;octet-stream&quot;, &quot;application&#x2F;x-msdownload&quot;, &quot;text&#x2F;html&quot;, &quot;application&#x2F;x-shockwave-flash&quot;],</span><br><span class=\"line\">              &quot;Transfer-Encoding&quot;: [&quot;chunked&quot;],</span><br><span class=\"line\">              &quot;Connection&quot;: [&quot;keep-alive&quot;],</span><br><span class=\"line\">              &quot;Pragma&quot;: &quot;no-cache&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &quot;outbound&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;protocol&quot;: &quot;freedom&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;settings&quot;: &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &quot;outboundDetour&quot;: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;protocol&quot;: &quot;blackhole&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;settings&quot;: &#123;&#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;tag&quot;: &quot;blocked&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ],</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &quot;routing&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;strategy&quot;: &quot;rules&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;settings&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;rules&quot;: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;type&quot;: &quot;field&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;ip&quot;: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;0.0.0.0&#x2F;8&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;10.0.0.0&#x2F;8&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;100.64.0.0&#x2F;10&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;127.0.0.0&#x2F;8&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;169.254.0.0&#x2F;16&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;172.16.0.0&#x2F;12&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;192.0.0.0&#x2F;24&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;192.0.2.0&#x2F;24&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;192.168.0.0&#x2F;16&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;198.18.0.0&#x2F;15&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;198.51.100.0&#x2F;24&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;203.0.113.0&#x2F;24&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;::1&#x2F;128&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;fc00::&#x2F;7&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;fe80::&#x2F;10&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          ],</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;outboundTag&quot;: &quot;blocked&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      ]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>运行后填入你要伪装的host就可以浪了，不过windows没有BBR加速，到了晚上延迟和速度就炸了。除非你的小鸡是 cn2 gia 的线路</p>\n<hr>\n<p>套CDN的配置（ws+tls）：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &quot;inbounds&quot;: [&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;port&quot;: 6666,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;listen&quot;: &quot;127.0.0.1&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;protocol&quot;: &quot;vmess&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;settings&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;clients&quot;: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;id&quot;: &quot;你的UUID&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;level&quot;: 1,</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;alterId&quot;: 64</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      ]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;streamSettings&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;network&quot;: &quot;ws&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;wsSettings&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;path&quot;: &quot;&#x2F;whatever&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;],</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &quot;outbounds&quot;: [&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;protocol&quot;: &quot;freedom&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;settings&quot;: &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;,&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;protocol&quot;: &quot;blackhole&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;settings&quot;: &#123;&#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;tag&quot;: &quot;blocked&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;],</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &quot;routing&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;rules&quot;: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;type&quot;: &quot;field&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;ip&quot;: [&quot;geoip:private&quot;],</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;outboundTag&quot;: &quot;blocked&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ]</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>地址填<code>127.0.0.1</code>因为是要跟<font color=\"#dd0000\">Nginx</font>相关联，只有<font color=\"#dd0000\">Nginx</font>可以访问</p>\n<p>其中Path地址<code>/whatever</code>需要记下来，也是要跟<font color=\"#dd0000\">Nginx</font>关联</p>\n<p>测试一下有没有运行成功：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">curl -i http:&#x2F;&#x2F;127.0.0.1:6666&#x2F;whatever</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">HTTP&#x2F;1.1 400 Bad Request</span><br><span class=\"line\">Content-Type: text&#x2F;plain; charset&#x3D;utf-8</span><br><span class=\"line\">Sec-Websocket-Version: 13</span><br><span class=\"line\">X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff</span><br><span class=\"line\">Date: Sun, 12 Jan 2020 11:45:14 GMT</span><br><span class=\"line\">Content-Length: 12</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Bad Request</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>出现400就是运行成功了</p>\n<p>至此，v2ray运行成功</p>\n<h3 id=\"二、申请ssl证书\">二、申请SSL证书<a title=\"#二、申请ssl证书\" href=\"#二、申请ssl证书\"></a></h3>\n<p>因为这里走的是套CDN的方案，走tls验证，就需要ssl证书了</p>\n<p>下载Certify The Web软件，<a href=\"https://certifytheweb.com/\" target=\"_blank\">飞机直达</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2021/image-20210106180503706.png\" alt=\"image-20210106180503706\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<ol>\n<li>新建证书</li>\n<li>增加域名</li>\n<li>申请证书</li>\n<li>OK，完成</li>\n</ol>\n<p>不过这软件申请的是IIS的证书，要导出来，改成Nginx能用的证书才行（具体度娘或谷哥）</p>\n<h3 id=\"三、安装配置nginx服务\">三、安装配置Nginx服务<a title=\"#三、安装配置nginx服务\" href=\"#三、安装配置nginx服务\"></a></h3>\n<p>下载Nginx的Windows版本</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://nginx.org/en/download.html\" target=\"_blank\">飞机直达</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2021/image-20210107092647864.png\" alt=\"image-20210107092647864\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p>解压后目录是这个样子</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2021/image-20210107092807891.png\" alt=\"image-20210107092807891\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p>进入<strong>conf</strong>文件夹，修改<strong>nginx.conf</strong>文件的配置</p>\n<p>新增<strong>Server</strong>服务配置</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">server &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    listen 443 ssl http2;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    server_name 你的域名;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    index index.html index.htm index.php;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    root 你的网站地址;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    ssl_certificate 证书内容crt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ssl_certificate_key 证书密钥key;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ssl_session_cache shared:SSL:10m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ssl_session_timeout 10m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ssl_protocols TLSv1.2 TLSv1.3;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ssl_prefer_server_ciphers on;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ssl_ciphers EECDH+AESGCM:EDH+AESGCM;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    location &#x2F;whatever &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    proxy_redirect off;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    proxy_http_version 1.1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    proxy_set_header Connection &quot;upgrade&quot;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    proxy_set_header Host $http_host;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    set $is_v2ray 0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if ($http_upgrade &#x3D; &quot;websocket&quot;) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        set $is_v2ray 1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    if ($is_v2ray &#x3D; 1) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        proxy_pass http:&#x2F;&#x2F;127.0.0.1:6666;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    if ($is_v2ray &#x3D; 0) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        rewrite ^&#x2F;(.*)$ &#x2F;mask-page last;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>将 <strong>server_name</strong>填上你的域名  <font color=\"#dd0000\">什么？还没有域名？那还不赶快去申请，怎么申请具体度娘或谷哥</font></p>\n<p><strong>ROOT</strong>填上你的网站地址，不用<strong>websocket</strong>访问时，假装你的<strong>v2ray</strong>就是一个网站</p>\n<p><strong>SSL</strong>填上刚刚用工具申请后，转换出来的证书</p>\n<p><font color=\"#dd0000\">其他信息不用改，当然，你想改也可以</font></p>\n<p>回到nginx解压目录</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">双击nginx.exe直接运行</span><br><span class=\"line\">或者 命令行 CD到解压目录输入命令</span><br><span class=\"line\">运行命令：</span><br><span class=\"line\">start nginx</span><br><span class=\"line\">停止命令：</span><br><span class=\"line\">nginx -s stop</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>测试一下有没有运行成功：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">curl -i https:&#x2F;&#x2F;你的域名&#x2F;whatever</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">HTTP&#x2F;1.1 400 Bad Request</span><br><span class=\"line\">Content-Type: text&#x2F;plain; charset&#x3D;utf-8</span><br><span class=\"line\">Sec-Websocket-Version: 13</span><br><span class=\"line\">X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff</span><br><span class=\"line\">Date: Sun, 12 Jan 2020 11:45:14 GMT</span><br><span class=\"line\">Content-Length: 12</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Bad Request</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>出现400就是运行成功了</p>\n<h3 id=\"四、套上cdn\">四、套上CDN<a title=\"#四、套上cdn\" href=\"#四、套上cdn\"></a></h3>\n<p>注册<strong>Cloudflare</strong> <a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/\" target=\"_blank\">飞机直达</a></p>\n<p><font color=\"#dd0000\">注册好Cloudflare了，就将它的页面关掉。不管它</font></p>\n<p>去到<strong>Cloudflare</strong>的托管网站  <a href=\"https://cdn.moeelf.com/\" target=\"_blank\">飞机直达</a> 用刚刚注册号的CF账号密码登陆进去</p>\n<h4 id=\"第一步：添加域名\">第一步：添加域名<a title=\"#第一步：添加域名\" href=\"#第一步：添加域名\"></a></h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2021/image-20210107094440721.png\" alt=\"image-20210107094440721\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"第二步：指向ip\">第二步：指向IP<a title=\"#第二步：指向ip\" href=\"#第二步：指向ip\"></a></h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2021/image-20210107100654234.png\" alt=\"image-20210107100654234\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"第三步：配置域名解析\">第三步：配置域名解析<a title=\"#第三步：配置域名解析\" href=\"#第三步：配置域名解析\"></a></h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2021/image-20210107095107391.png\" alt=\"image-20210107095107391\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"第四步：优化路由\">第四步：优化路由<a title=\"#第四步：优化路由\" href=\"#第四步：优化路由\"></a></h4>\n<p><font color=\"#dd0000\">看到第三步的截图，有境内A记录线路、联通电信A记录线路。我就知道你想要问什么了</font></p>\n<ul>\n<li>首先，套上了Cloudflare的CDN，其实它默认给的IP也并不是最适合你的，可能有些IP会很慢，有些可能还正在富强，正在接受教育</li>\n<li>所以，Cloudflare的IP有千千万万个，要从那么多的IP中筛选出适合你网络的IP使用，才能体现CDN的效果，不然更加龟速</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/badafans/better-cloudflare-ip\" target=\"_blank\">IP筛选工具链接</a></p>\n<p>我们选择windows版本</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/Qinin/my-image/raw/master/2021/image-20210107095854119.png\" alt=\"image-20210107095854119\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p>筛选出合适的IP之后，填到域名解析这里即可，参照第三步截图</p>\n<p>至此套CDN教程结束</p>\n<h3 id=\"五、连接上v2ray客户端\">五、连接上V2ray客户端<a title=\"#五、连接上v2ray客户端\" href=\"#五、连接上v2ray客户端\"></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/2dust/v2rayN\" target=\"_blank\">Windows版直链</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/2dust/v2rayNG\" target=\"_blank\">Android版直链</a></p>\n<p>配置填写：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br><span class=\"line\">74</span><br><span class=\"line\">75</span><br><span class=\"line\">76</span><br><span class=\"line\">77</span><br><span class=\"line\">78</span><br><span class=\"line\">79</span><br><span class=\"line\">80</span><br><span class=\"line\">81</span><br><span class=\"line\">82</span><br><span class=\"line\">83</span><br><span class=\"line\">84</span><br><span class=\"line\">85</span><br><span class=\"line\">86</span><br><span class=\"line\">87</span><br><span class=\"line\">88</span><br><span class=\"line\">89</span><br><span class=\"line\">90</span><br><span class=\"line\">91</span><br><span class=\"line\">92</span><br><span class=\"line\">93</span><br><span class=\"line\">94</span><br><span class=\"line\">95</span><br><span class=\"line\">96</span><br><span class=\"line\">97</span><br><span class=\"line\">98</span><br><span class=\"line\">99</span><br><span class=\"line\">100</span><br><span class=\"line\">101</span><br><span class=\"line\">102</span><br><span class=\"line\">103</span><br><span class=\"line\">104</span><br><span class=\"line\">105</span><br><span class=\"line\">106</span><br><span class=\"line\">107</span><br><span class=\"line\">108</span><br><span class=\"line\">109</span><br><span class=\"line\">110</span><br><span class=\"line\">111</span><br><span class=\"line\">112</span><br><span class=\"line\">113</span><br><span class=\"line\">114</span><br><span class=\"line\">115</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &quot;dns&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;hosts&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;domain:googleapis.cn&quot;: &quot;googleapis.com&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;servers&quot;: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;1.1.1.1&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ]</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &quot;inbounds&quot;: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;listen&quot;: &quot;127.0.0.1&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;port&quot;: 10808,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;protocol&quot;: &quot;socks&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;settings&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;auth&quot;: &quot;noauth&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;udp&quot;: true,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;userLevel&quot;: 8</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;sniffing&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;destOverride&quot;: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;http&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;tls&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ],</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;enabled&quot;: true</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;tag&quot;: &quot;socks&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;listen&quot;: &quot;127.0.0.1&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;port&quot;: 10809,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;protocol&quot;: &quot;http&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;settings&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;userLevel&quot;: 8</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;tag&quot;: &quot;http&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ],</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &quot;log&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;loglevel&quot;: &quot;warning&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &quot;outbounds&quot;: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;mux&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;concurrency&quot;: -1,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;enabled&quot;: false</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;protocol&quot;: &quot;vmess&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;settings&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;vnext&quot;: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;address&quot;: &quot;你的域名&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;port&quot;: 443,</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;users&quot;: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">              &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &quot;alterId&quot;: 64,</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &quot;id&quot;: &quot;你的UUID&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &quot;level&quot;: 8,</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &quot;security&quot;: &quot;auto&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">              &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            ]</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ]</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;streamSettings&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;network&quot;: &quot;ws&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;security&quot;: &quot;tls&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;tlsSettings&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;allowInsecure&quot;: false,</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;serverName&quot;: &quot;你的域名&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;wsSettings&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;headers&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &quot;Host&quot;: &quot;你的域名&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;path&quot;: &quot;&#x2F;whatever&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;tag&quot;: &quot;proxy&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;protocol&quot;: &quot;freedom&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;settings&quot;: &#123;&#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;tag&quot;: &quot;direct&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;protocol&quot;: &quot;blackhole&quot;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;settings&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;response&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          &quot;type&quot;: &quot;http&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;tag&quot;: &quot;block&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ],</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &quot;policy&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;levels&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;8&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;connIdle&quot;: 300,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;downlinkOnly&quot;: 1,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;handshake&quot;: 4,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &quot;uplinkOnly&quot;: 1</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;system&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;statsOutboundUplink&quot;: true,</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &quot;statsOutboundDownlink&quot;: true</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &quot;routing&quot;: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &quot;domainStrategy&quo